fields.name: Alpine Drive Mansionette
fields.description: Extraordinary scale, soaring ceilings and natural light embody this newer contemporary oasis. Perfectly situated on a sprawling northern lot in the 500 block of the highly coveted Alpine Drive, this 6,500 square foot estate boasts grand entertaining spaces, 6 generous bedrooms, and an expansive upstairs family room, dedicated office, gym, entertaining bar, breakfast nook, indoor water feature, and stunning walnut staircase.

fields.name: 4 bedfroom Country House
fields.description: Carriage Drive is found on a delightful and quiet backwater within Littleborough, accessed via a private lane offering superb privacy with the grounds not being overlooked. Though the property offers such tranquillity it is far from isolated being within walking distance of Littleborough town centre and its array of amenities which include a train station offering ease of access to both Leeds and Manchester.

fields.name: 7 bedroom Norfolk House
fields.description: Wilby Hall is a significant late 16th century part moated country house, Grade II Listed and wonderfully positioned at the heart of its own 12 acres of mature gardens and grounds. The house is architecturally distinguished, built of mellow red brick with crow stepped gables, mullioned and transomed windows which retain much of the original glass, and fine internal period detail.

fields.name: Hereford Mansion
fields.description: A magnificent Georgian House with fine landscaped gardens and lake at the heart of an idyllic country estate. Coach House, Victorian stable block, manege and paddocks, beautiful restored productive walled garden, 11 flats, cottages and farmhouses, parkland and woodland, working farms.

fields.name: Charmilon Lane Mansion
fields.description: Exquisite Custom Gated Contemporary Estate in prime Encino.  Amazing View lot with jetliner views.  Over 11,000 sqft of luxury living on ¾ of an acre.  6 luxury en suite bedrooms, 10 bathrooms all with the finest finishes and perfection of design.  The grand living room boasts a floating staircase, ceilings soaring over 30+ ft with a wall of windows overlooking the San Fernando Valley. Incredible open floor plan. Sumptuous master suite is a 1500

fields.name: Amalfi Drive Castle
fields.description: A spectacular Mediterranean estate on almost 1/2 acre in the Riviera. Exquisite craftsmanship, dramatic 2-story entry with wood-beam ceiling, French doors throughout, 3 fireplaces, limestone floors, crown molding, wine cellar, center hall plan with 5 bedroom suites. Master with fireplace, his & hers marble baths, gym, sitting room, or guest suite with separate entrance.

fields.name: Beverly Drive Mansion
fields.address: 1021 N. BEVERLY DR., BEVERLY HILLS, CA 90210
fields.description: A sprawling Beverly Hills contemporary estate on over 1 acre of land, recently completed with meticulous attention to design and detail. Developed by Sen Properties, the 7 beds, 10 baths main residence boasts 15,605 sq. ft. of stylish living spaces including an elegant foyer, top-of-the-line chef’s kitchen, sleek dining and living areas, state-of-the-art movie theater and gym, wine cellar, a lavish owner’s suite with his-and-hers walk-in closets

fields.name: Meadowgate Mansion
fields.description: An exquisite 9,200+ sq. ft. estate set on nearly a half-acre of land in the prime Royal Oaks neighborhood of Encino. Features 5 en-suite bedrooms and 7 bathrooms with European craftsmanship throughout, including walnut hardwood floors, custom wall coverings and Venetian plaster ceilings. Incredible professional chef's kitchen with Carrara marble counters and backsplash, walk-in pantry and breakfast bar, all leading to the magnificent great room.

fields.name: Sydney Beachside Mansion
fields.address: 25 Thyra Road Sydney, New South Wales, 2108 Australia
fields.description: urrounded by nature, this superb lifestyle property offers more a way of life than simply a place to stay, and represents a rare opportunity to witness a slice of paradise and become a part of a privileged beachside enclave in one of Palm Beach's most sought-after positions.

fields.name: Castillo Caribe
fields.description: Castillo Caribe offers a rare opportunity to combine this with privacy, security, luxury and lifestyle all on a pristine white sandy beach overlooking the crystal clear waters of the Caribbean Sea.

fields.name: The White House
fields.description: There are 132 rooms, 35 bathrooms, and 6 levels in the Residence. There are also 412 doors, 147 windows, 28 fireplaces, 8 staircases, and 3 elevators.The White House kitchen is able to serve dinner to as many as 140 guests and hors d'oeuvres to more than 1,000. The White House requires 570 gallons of paint to cover its outside surface.

fields.name: Tha Dogg House
fields.description: The rap legend's mansion is located in the gated community of County Estates; a supposedly middle-class suburb that sits on a cul-de-sac. The house takes up 2.8 acres of land, having a square footage of 4,000. Sources reported that the mansion has 4 beds and 4 baths, as well as a pool and spa area, as well as a basketball court. The estate is said to be full of panoramic views at every angle. The mansion sounds like everyone's dream house.

fields.name: Kensington Town House
fields.description: The refurbishment this Grade ll listed detached 1862 Stucco house in Kensington has started on site.

fields.name: Laurelwood Drive Mansion
fields.description: The newly-built Studio City retreat featured on season two and three, and was hard to shift mainly due to its steeply sloping driveway and lack of car parking space. Situated on a secluded plot behind private gates, the ultra-secure home is entirely bespoke and benefits from high-end interior design and custom finishes throughout.

fields.name: Beckham Manor House
fields.description: It"s easy to see why the family spend so much time there; as well as having stunning interiors with log-burning fires and exposed brick walls, the country retreat has incredible gardens with a pool, tennis court and sauna.

fields.name: Paris Town House
fields.description: In a prestigious, calm and secure district of the 16th arrondissement of Paris, on a closed square, stands behind a historic facade, a newly built and inimitable 1,237 sqm property. This house contains an extremely comfortable interior with the best of the latest modern features, pleasant volumes and nice large windows allowing natural light in, just like the original glass roof.

fields.name: Luxury Swiss Chalet
fields.description: Located away from prying eyes, in the heart of the village, a few steps from the ski slopes and at the end of a private road, the Chalet Fleur des Neiges dominates with a breathtaking view of the Dents du Midi chain.

fields.name: Extraordinary German Villa
fields.description: In the sought-after district of Ammerland, on a sun-drenched plot of land directly at Lake Starnberg, a prestigious manor house is for sale that offers the best conditions for fulfilling long-cherished life and living dreams. A historical villa with about 375 sqm living space and about 137 sqm usable area awaits you, which is embedded in a secluded park property with flowering hedges, large trees, comfortable outdoor seats and well-kept English lawns.

fields.name: Belmont Estate
fields.description: From the very arrival, the porte-cochère entrance and stone waterfall are part of the detailing that create the exceptional experience that one has from being here. Dramatic, solid oak cathedral doors flank the home"s entrance, you find yourself standing still in the grand hallway where light, glass, art, and soaring ceilings prevail over any expectations. You understand the display that this room offers, which among many things contains a striking French Ormolu chandelier, a grand piano and grand hall which has been played in by world class musicians.

fields.name: Santiago"s Most Exclusive Property
fields.description: Exclusive property of the renowned architect De Groote in the top of Lo Curro neighbourhood, with an impressive panoramic view that dominates the city strip and mountain range. An imposing access flanked by large palm trees leads to the property´s entrance which receives visitors with it´s wonderful carved wooden doors. Distribution hall with marble floor and wooden marquetry, leads to the elegant living room with parquet floors, high ceilings, upholstered walls and vaulted ceilings with hand-painted wood.

fields.name: Atelier House
fields.description: Atelier House is a stunning Caribbean retreat. The design was conceptualised in close collaboration with the interior architect / owner, who has completed projects for discerning homeowners in London, France, Italy and Kenya. The dramatic double-height living space maximizes the stunning views which extend beyond the outdoor terraces and pool across a mahogany tree-filled gully to the Caribbean Sea. In addition to the ground-level terraces and 32 x 27 ft. pool there is a large roof terrace and mezzanine-level study offering stunning views of the West Coast.

fields.name: Coin de Mire Gate Villa
fields.description: This stunning seven-bedroom luxury beachfront villa overlooking the nature reserve islet, Coin de Mire, offers the ultimate luxurious island lifestyle.The beautifully appointed open plan ground floor living area opens out entirely to a landscaped garden and pool deck with a jacuzzi and water feature. Relax on a lounger on balmy summer days and watch the boats sail past or stroll across the grass verge and dive into the azure ocean.

fields.name: Point Piper
fields.description: First time offered in 20 years. It is unique, it is unrivalled. A Residence of inspiration and unsurpassed grandeur. Breathtakingly executed to a finite degree. Set in a private oasis right on Seven Shillings Beach. Back dropped by idyllic Bay & Harbour views from the beach to the Opera House, Harbour Bridge and beyond. Accompanied by Sydney's most coveted 'Pagoda' Boathouse and calm, deepwater berth for year round mooring. This masterpiece of residential architecture, designed by Richard Christian and Walter Barda, indulges every possible personal extravagance, need, whim and necessity.

fields.name: Karuizawa Residence
fields.description: This unique Japanese home is the swap for you. It"s absolutely huge and has a massive wine celler for you to get drunk with all your mates.

fields.name: Moscow Penthouse
fields.description: Luxury apartments are located on the 69th floor of Federation Towers. Platinum apartments - from the 91st floor. Penthouse occupies 95-97 floors. At this height, exceptional views - only the sky around you. According to the international classification of skyscrapers "Federation Tower" is an ultra-high skyscraper - its height is 374 meters. Real panoramic windows - from wall to wall, from floor to ceiling, without bars and handrails. Nothing prevents you from enjoying the stunning lively paintings of Moscow.

fields.name: Casa Corazon
fields.description: Casa Corazón is a property with a great personality and unique style, on it you can appreciate design details in every corner, as impressive palapas, domes on the bedrooms, glass art work in bathroom, orchide’s greenhouse, robust solid wood beams, handmade talavera and industrial equipment in kitchen, traditional roof tile, bright colors on walls and large windows.

fields.name: 10 Bed Danish Home
fields.description: Copenhagens most beautiful Townhouse. This historic city townhouse dating back to 1908 is located in the beautiful Ambassador quarter in Hellerup, a mere 7 minutes from Kongens Nytorv. It is situated on a sun-drenched plot with freshly landscaped gardens in a charming up-scale residential neighborhood. The villa has been completely restored to its original splendor, while simultaneously incorporating powerful modernization and a totally customized design experience.

fields.name: Constantia
fields.description: This breathtaking property set on 3.5 acres is the epitome of comfort, quality and the very best architectural design all set in a beautifully landscaped garden. Something unique in Constantia with creature comforts, up-to the minute sophistication, state of the art functionality and stylish simplicity . Entertain your guests effortlessly in one of the many entertainment rooms, keep fit in your private gym with lap pool all while enjoying views that seem to go on forever from every aspect of this home.

fields.name: Soria
fields.description: With 470,000 M2 of land and 46,000 M2 of construction, Soria also has a sophisticated and captivating 16-bedroom Hacienda. The rooms are decorated with elegant antiques, 9 spacious and comfortable Villas that once housed distinguished visitors as well as European engineers who reviewed machinery and trained personnel in the nearby factories. Extensive and wooded green areas surround both the Hacienda and the 9 blocks that make up the 247 modest homes that at the time were built for the employees who worked in the factories.

fields.name: Innerwick House
fields.description: Considered Edinburgh’s finest private home this highly prized Georgian mansion is a once-in-a-generation opportunity and arguably the very best family home in Edinburgh. The house is located in the affluent and prestigious Murrayfield area, especially sought after for its close proximity to world-class schools for every age group. This outstanding property dates back to the 1800’s.

fields.name: Seafield House
fields.description: An attractive mid-18th Century mansion, built circa 1730. Magically positioned within some 80 acres or 32 hectares on the shores of Malahide Estuary, on the periphery of Dublin city and within a 15 minute drive of Dublin International airport. Enjoying an idyllic position within glorious private grounds the water views over Malahide Estuary are exceptional and the mature Victorian designed gardens and stone outbuildings include a magnificent walled garden, a Yew Walk and an attractive cut-stone enclosed stable yard.

fields.name: Penthouse on Delfim Moreira
fields.description: The penthouse is a project by Luiz Fernando Redó, with a main hall with more than 100 s.m., besides a TV room. In the intimate area, there are five bedrooms with closet. Each one with more than 50 s.m., and the master with more than 100 s.m., large closet and two bathrooms. Lunch room, kitchen, pantry and employee's room. On the second floor, there is a terrace with swimming pool, sauna and barbecue grill.

fields.name: Coach House
fields.description: Set on a cliff overlooking the sea, this stately country manor offers stunning panoramic views from all angles. Designed with the tropical climate in mind and constructed to world-class standards, the Manor combines luxury and comfort in a magnificent coastal setting. Dubbed by many as the Most Beautiful House in Bohol, this is truly an impressive property in an exceptional location. Situated in Brgy. Catarman, Dauis on Panglao Island in Bohol, a short drive from the new Panglao-Bohol International Airport. Escaping to this exclusive retreat couldn’t be any easier.

fields.name: The Leela Sky Villas
fields.description: The stunning development offers 8 BHK penthouses with a built-up area of 9,733.92 Sq. Ft. It is the first mix use development in New Delhi with a step in shopping mall, food courts, showrooms, offices and movie theaters with multi-level lift parking. These are also the first residences in India with a 4-meter floor to floor height with the highest planned recreational club/restro bar club with a provision of helipad. Additionally, the observatory area on top gives residents an expansive and breathtaking 360-degree view of Delhi.

fields.name: Chameleon villa
fields.description: A unique architecture and design offered by the Chameleon villa in the exclusive area of Son Vida, with breathtaking views to the sea, the city and the harbor of Palma. The Chameleon house attracts through its exceptional light effects, which accomplish a true miracle of light; finest crystal on which surface has been installed a special LED technology, can be programmed in its colors corresponding to your wish. The villa consists of three buildings.

fields.name: Casuarinas
fields.description: Beautiful house with pool and garden by Architect Roberto Río Frió in Casuarinas closed condominium with 4 bedrooms in suite. All of the spaces have wooden floors. The entrance hall is modern and has elegant wooden finishings and a panoramic view from the top of Casuarinas. This hall brings us to the main living room and separate dining room with very tall ceilings Both have a beatiful view of the pool, terrace and garden. There is a living room in this first floor as well as the kitchen. It comes fully equipped and has modern finishings and a daily dining area.

fields.name: 6 Bedroom Flat
fields.description: Unique apartment on the 24 de Julho Avenue, with six bedrooms which stands out for its location facing the Tagus river in downtown Lisbon, in an area that has seen total rehabilitation, with shops, bars and restaurants. Condominium with Concierge Service, 5 * Hotel Lobby, Spa with indoor pool for residents and an architectural 'concept' which is absolutely unique in the city. The penthouses have private elevators, terraces with unique views of the city and the river, private pool and luxury finishes.

fields.name: Hampton Hall
fields.description: A beautifully designed Manor House in the prestigious Crown Estate with over 70 rooms, including staff accommodation, internal and external leisure facilities, a two storey garage and unsurpassed luxury.

fields.name: Barcelona Apartment
fields.description: It has a large living room with high ceilings with moldings and access to three balconies with wonderful views of Paseo de Gracia and La Pedrera. The apartment is in an impeccable condition with finishes of the highest quality. After being reformed, all the apartments were emptied making them brand new to the most demanding level of comfort.

fields.name: Stunning Lakehouse
fields.description: Gorgeous lakefront trophy estate, featuring a generous garden and beautiful outdoor and indoor pools. With 7 bedrooms, this lakeside beauty is the perfect place for you and your family to stay. The perfect place to escape the city and relax by the peaceful and famous Lake Como.

fields.name: The perfect Capri Getaway
fields.description: Built during the second half of the 18th century, on the ruins of a Roman Palace, inhabited by artists of different molds, painters, musicians, composers, the sumptuous Villa Bismarck, takes its name from its most famous owner, the Countess Mona Strader Bismarck. The villa, one of the most beautiful in the world, enjoys a privileged location on the island of Capri.

fields.name: Beautiful Parisian Townhouse Mansion
fields.description: This exceptional private mansion from the 18th century is close to Musée d’Orsay. Raised on the basement, it is built on five levels and has a generous living space. It has kept the charm of yesteryear as shown with the superb wood paneling from regency period, the Venetian paintings in the three reception rooms of the first floor and the painted Ottoman wood paneling in the boudoir. A wonderful main staircase from the 18th century leads to the whole property

fields.name: Madrid Penthouse
fields.description: Wonderful penthouse with large terraces. It is located in a classical building with an excellent location and an interior that has been completely refurbished with an excellent eye for detail, respecting its classical façade. It boasts an unusual sense of peacefulness and brightness.The building includes several common areas such as a bright sophisticated gymnasium, swimming pool, cinema, wine cellar, communal kitchen

fields.name: Italian Neo-Classical Villa
fields.description: Historic villa dating back to the late 19th century in the typical late-Renaissance Tuscan style dominating all over the valley of Pistoia. Conveniently and strategically located in less than 25 min. from Florence and just over 40 min. from the prestigious coastline of Versilia.

fields.name: Palmilla Beachfront Cabo
fields.description: Palmilla Beachfront Six is a one-of-a-kind property on the beach from the ample backyard pool and luscious garden areas. This home is an architectural gem, designed and built in a stunning Spanish-Colonial style that combines the highest standards in Mexican materials, finishes, décor and craftmanship.

fields.name: Fifth Avenue Apartment
fields.description: Full-floor Fifth Avenue apartment with approximately 5,500 square feet, four exposures and exquisite Central Park views centered just above Conservatory Pond. Perfect place for family to come and stay and see the sights of New York.

fields.name: St Tropez Villa
fields.description: Stunning 7 bedroom villa, which is probably one of the most amazing properties to stay within the Saint-Tropez peninsula, ideally situated in a quiet and sunny setting, yet close to the village and the beaches.

fields.name: Stunning French Chalet
fields.description: The chalet is made up of 4 bedrooms with adjoining bathrooms and two duplexes located on the ground floor, like chalets on the roof with large volumes under roofs for master bedrooms and lounges. Each chalet has independent basements with parking lots, cellars and storage for skis and snowboards equipped with boot dryers. A common relaxation area includes a fitness center and a sauna with relaxation area and shower.

fields.name: Beautiful Ibizan Villa
fields.description: This luxury villa is located in the north of Ibiza, near the well known beach Cala Benirras.The house is in a very quiet area, surrounded by woods, for a very relaxing holiday and enjoys breathtaking views to the sea and the sunset.Every bedroom overlooks the sea.The lovely town of San Miquel is just few km away.

fields.name: Secluded Ibizan Finca
fields.description: This home is the ideal property for anyone interested in being in the middle of nature secluded from any neighbors or noise from road traffic. This property is a family friendly home.

fields.name: Provence Chateau
fields.description: A stunning french chateau situated in the middle of the provence hills. The perfect place for anyone to get away from the business of the city and relax in this french paradise.

fields.name: Corfu Beachside Mansion
fields.description: The stunning property offers breathtaking views of the Ionian sea and enjoys a most -desired feeling of privacy in all its areas. With 12 bedrooms, the property is big enough to accomodate lots of guests and families.

fields.name: Aleomandra, Mykonos, 84600
fields.description: Casa Reale, defining elegance, sophistication and style, in a scenic setting with breathtaking sea views.Admire by day the endless blue horizon stretching as far as the eye can see and marvel at nature’s brush strokes painting the sky in shades of red and gold, as the sun slowly sets. A veritable kaleidoscope of wondrous colour.
